		(title "50_LIGHT_POWER_TOP - PCB-E_LIGHT_POWER")
		(date "2026-07-16")
		(rev "A3")
		(company "Gonoboben/plataVM")
		(comment 1 "V1.6 PCB-E boundary: local PWM/current control, CAN-FD setpoints and direct HARD_OFF")
		(comment 2 "Detailed hierarchy 51..56; no driver controller, magnetics, connectors or footprints selected")
	)
	(lib_symbols)
	(text "50_LIGHT_POWER_TOP - V1.6 HIERARCHY MAP\nPCB-E receives PACK_BUS_LIGHT_IN and drives six independent LED loads in two symmetric zones 2x3.\nEach channel has local current regulation, local PWM generation, fault detection and current diagnostics.\nFunctional input range is 8..16 V; default safe state is all channels OFF."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 12 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.26 1.26)) (justify left))
		(uuid "light-v16-50-101")
	)
	(text "LOCAL CONTROL / TRANSPORT\nCAN-FD carries LIGHT_BRANCH_EN, brightness setpoints and detailed channel diagnostics. Six high-frequency PWM lines do not traverse the interboard harness.\nLocal PWM is 3.3 V active-high, default 1 kHz, configurable 100..1000 Hz. LIGHT_GROUP_HARD_OFF is a direct hardware input."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 84 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.08 1.08)) (justify left))
		(uuid "light-v16-50-102")
	)
	(text "SUB-SHEETS 51..56\n51 input protection; 52 driver template; 53 channels 1..3; 54 channels 4..6; 55 local diagnostics/data aggregation; 56 LED output/CAN/hard-line connector boundary.\nLIGHT_BOARD_FAULT_N is a direct summary output to PCB-B."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 150 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.08 1.08)) (justify left))
		(uuid "light-v16-50-103")
	)
	(text "FAIL-SAFE / POWER RULES\nLocal short/open/overcurrent/thermal protection remains active without CAN-FD. HARD_OFF overrides all setpoints.\nA single-channel fault should remain isolated unless group thermal protection requires wider shutdown.\nFull simultaneous light operation remains subject to the unresolved system power budget."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12 212 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.08 1.08)) (justify left))
		(uuid "light-v16-50-104")
	)
